<plot>A bachelor account executive with an advertising agency, thinks he has the perfect set-up with three girlfriends. And then there is Marion his devoted secretary who worships him and will do anything for him. Steve Allen wrote the music and lyrics to the songs which are, "This Could Be the Start of Something", "Slave Girl", "The Girl in the Grey Flannel Suit", "I'm Simply Starved", "Rogue Male", "Three Cheers and a Tiger", "One Man Woman", "Impossible", and "Little Black Book". A very entertaining musical comedy.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?521572</url></doc>
